{
  "stem": "11964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had one proof of it when we came back after we would liberated to that gentlemen where-- to whom my parents entrusted the silver and the fur who denied ever getting it, and who wouldn't give it back to us.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the ghetto was a very, very restrictive, and a very restricting area, where we really had a very, a very limited space.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only the actual living space, but actually, also, the limited outside space.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that ghetto was keeping to-- keeping us very much together in, in, in a way that it brought us together as well.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would try to establish semblance of a social life, semblance of an intellectual life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, there were no schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my younger sister was very young, and I knew that she needed education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I established a clandestine school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the girls would come to my room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't call it an apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would be in groups of five or sixes, and they would come every hour on the hour.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we would-- I would conduct classes with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I would spill out of my head whatever I remembered having learned in my school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the most incongruous subject matters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I would teach them Latin vocabulary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I would teach them geography.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I would, I would teach them anything I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I wrote an essay, which I call 'Gone with a Dream' because one of the things that I read most recently, when-- prior to establishing the school, was the Polish translation of And when the girls came-- and they were so solemn, and they were so sorrowful.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they would say, please, please tell us a story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I would say, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
